  <verse number="11" style="v" />For the grace of God has appeared to all people. 

  <verse number="12" style="v" />It trains us to deny ungodliness and worldly passions. It trains us to live sensibly, righteously, and in a godly way in this age

  <verse number="13" style="v" />while we look forward to receiving our blessed hope, the appearance of the glory of our great God and Savior Jesus Christ.
